## Build Order — Phase by Phase

Build and fully test each phase before starting the next.
Do not build Screen 3 if Screen 2 has broken buttons.

**Phase 1 — Shared components**
floatInput, otpRow, buttons (primary/secondary/ghost), icon(), logo(),
sbar(), tbar(), navbar(), switchPill(), faceChip(), faceChipsRow(),
filterBar(), actionTabs(), photoIllustration(), photoGrid(), photoCell(),
bottomSheet(), toast(), popup(), eventCard()

Test: render each component in isolation. Confirm inputs work. Confirm buttons fire.

**Phase 2 — Varun's full journey**
entry → varun-reg → varun-otp → varun-profile →
varun-home → varun-create-group → varun-sync → varun-tagging → varun-home

- Journey starts from `screenEntry` (journey selector card — tap Varun card → `go('varun-reg')`)
- Journey ends at `screenVarunHome` after sharing completes — this is the closure state
- LIVE album card on home taps → `taggingOpenTab='group'; go('varun-tagging')` (Group tab active)
- "Add memories" button → `taggingOpenTab='my-photos'; go('varun-tagging')` (My Photos tab active)
- `taggingOpenTab` is a global consumed once in `screenVarunTagging()` reset block

Test every interaction on varun-event:
- Face chips scroll and toggle filter
- My Photos / With Me tabs switch content
- Filter bar category tap shows sub-chips
- Sub-chip tap dims non-matching photos
- Long press photo enters selection mode
- Share FAB appears when photos are selected
- Every option in share sheet responds
- Download sheet shows ₹5 and ₹149 pricing
- Remove shows destructive popup
- Single tap photo opens full screen
- Full screen prev/next navigation works
- Identification sheet opens on tap of unidentified person avatar (contextual, not auto-triggered)
- Inline search bar expands in top bar on search icon tap (no new screen)
- Delivery screen progress animates to completion

**Phase 3 — Remaining journeys**
Beulah: beulah-scene → beulah-web → beulah-reg → beulah-otp → beulah-photos
