### postRender hook
No auto-fire timers for varun-tagging. Identification is contextual — triggered only when the
user taps an unidentified person avatar. screenVarunTagging() resets all tagging globals at the
top of the function so each visit starts clean.

### Selection mode — in-place DOM mutation pattern
Top bar swap (no re-render):
- Enter: `document.getElementById('tagging-top-bar').innerHTML = 'Cancel ... X selected ...'`
- Exit: `taggingRestoreTopBar()` rebuilds the original back/title/icons HTML

Checkbox visibility: `check-{id}` divs always exist in DOM; `display:none` ↔ `display:flex`

Share FAB: pill button (`id="tagging-share-fab"`, `border-radius:24px`) with share icon + `<span id="tagging-fab-label">`. Label updates live: "Share (1)" on enter, "Share (N)" on each tap toggle. `display:none` ↔ `display:flex` toggled by `taggingEnterSelect` / `taggingExitSelect`. Consistent across ALL tabs (Group, Saved, Downloaded, My Photos) — positioned absolute within the screen, independent of grid content.

### Group tab (formerly Group Pool)
Tab IDs: `['group', 'saved', 'downloaded', 'my-photos']` — in that order, left to right.
Active tab style: `color:T.blue`, `fontWeight:600`, `border-bottom:2px solid T.blue`.

- `taggingSetTab('group')` rebuilds `#tagging-grid` with pool photos using `taggingPhotoCell()` — selection/long-press works on Group tab exactly as on My Photos
- Any other tab also rebuilds full grid via `taggingPhotoCell()`
- Badge: `#ttab-group-badge` span inside the Group tab button; updated by `doShareWithGroup`
- `groupPoolCount` — user's contributed photo count (starts 12, caps at 34)
- `groupDisplayCount` — total group pool count across all members (starts 258, increments on share)
- `doShareWithGroup()` increments both; badge shows `groupDisplayCount`

