## Test Gate — Run After Every Screen

Before moving to the next screen, verify:

1. Every input field — tap it, type, confirm label floats up and stays up
2. Every button — tap it, confirm it responds (navigates, opens sheet, shows toast)
3. Every sheet — open it, tap every option inside, confirm no blocking
4. Back button — confirm it returns to the correct previous screen
5. Switch Journey pill — confirm it's visible and returns to entry
6. No dead ends — every tappable element does something

If any item fails — fix it before proceeding. This rule is non-negotiable.

