## Common Mistakes — Do Not Repeat

| What went wrong | What to do instead |
|---|---|
| CSS ~ selector for floating label | JS inline style on onfocus/onblur |
| Single hidden 1px OTP input | 6 real `<input>` elements |
| Sheet overlay blocking sheet buttons | `onclick="event.stopPropagation()"` on inner card |
| photoTap() only works in selection mode | Single tap always opens full screen |
| FAB as flex child of nav bar | FAB is `position:absolute` inside `position:relative` nav bar |
| Fixed 844px height on mobile | `100svh` with `100vh` fallback via `@supports` |
| Missing My Photos / With Me tabs | Required in every event screen — see structure above |
| Moving to next screen before testing current | Test gate after every screen, no exceptions |
| Rewriting a function and losing dependent functions | Search for all callers before rewriting anything |
| Black `#111` desktop background | Use `#E8E4DF` warm grey |
| Filter chips that render but don't respond | Use real `<button>` elements with `onclick`, not styled divs |
| Suggestion chips in Moment B that don't fill input | Use fillMomBName() with direct style manipulation |
